         <abstract>
            <p>This paper presents formulas for the long-term annualized periodic return, the expected annualized periodic return, and the variance of annualized periodic returns for two popular option strategies--stock plus put (portfolio insurance) and stock minus call (covered write). These formulas can be used to resolve several misconceptions about the two strategies.</p>
